These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, drama, animation, action
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, daisy, aconite
1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | action | animation | drama | martial-arts   |
| Flower   | tulip  | rose     | daisy   | aconite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, quad-bike, boat
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, amaryllis, aconite
1. the person driving the boat is the person who growstulip##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | quad-bike | boat | airplane | scooter    |
| Flower   | amaryllis    | tulip      | daffodil | aconite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cycling, soccer, baseball
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, aquamarine, turquise, grey
1. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Sport         | tennis | baseball | soccer   | cycling |
| Color   | apricot   | turquise | grey | aquamarine         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
House: palace, victorian, tower, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, mechanic, accountant, software-developer
1. the mechanic is the farmhouse house##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the accountant##1
3. the victorian house is on the left of the palace house##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the pilot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| House   | farmhouse | victorian | palace  | tower      |
| Job         | mechanic | software-developer   | accountant | pilot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, australian, pakistani, french
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, february, august, june
1. the australian is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the pakistani##1
3. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Nationality   | french | pakistani | australian | indonesian |
| Birthday    | april       | june | august | february     |

