.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, photography, hiking, chess
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, february, march, june
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | chess | hiking | gardening | photography |
| Birthday           | january      | march | june | february    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, adventure, action, disaster
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, townhouse, tower
1. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | adventure | fantasy | disaster  |
| House           | townhouse | craftsman | tower       | gothic-revival |

