.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, mystery, western, thriller
City: marseilles, san-francisco, edinburgh, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person traveling to venice is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | western | martial-arts      | mystery | thriller |
| City   | marseilles          | san-francisco | edinburgh     | venice    |

