.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, aristoff, siglo, dunhill
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, analyst, nurse, architect
1. the architect is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the analyst is on the left of the nurse##1
5. the architect is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | aristoff    | siglo       | alhambra | dunhill   |
| Job     | analyst | nurse | architect   | lawyer |

