.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, soul, hip-hop, country
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, october, june
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Music-Genre    | metal | hip-hop  | soul | country |
| Birthday   | june | october | april          | september    |

