.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, blend, game, tiparillo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, october, january
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the blend-smoker is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Cigar      | game | blend  | ritmeester | tiparillo |
| Birthday   | may  | october | january           | september   |

