.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, canasta, monopoly
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, police-officer, firefighter, paramedic
1. the paramedic is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the firefighter is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the firefighter is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Game   | poker | scrabble | monopoly | canasta  |
| Job           | paramedic | police-officer      | firefighter | software-developer |

