3. the person playing billiard is the paramedic##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the scientist##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Game   | billiard | poker  | domino | snooker   |
| Job        | paramedic | scientist | nurse    | librarian |

