.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-14::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, cat, frog, mouse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, iced-tea, fanta
1. the owner of the fish is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the owner of the cat is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet          | fish | frog  | cat  | mouse |
| Beverage   | water   | cola | iced-tea | fanta   |

