.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, gardening, rock-climbing, collecting
There 4 different types of food: papaya, artichoke, mango, apricot
1. the person eating apricot is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is the person eating artichoke##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | gardening      | rock-climbing | collecting | chess |
| Food     | papaya | apricot    | mango  | artichoke |

