.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, firefighter, videographer, fisherman
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the videographer is on the left of the fisherman##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the videographer##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Job         | firefighter | videographer | fisherman | lawyer |
| Pet   | turtle     | mouse    | hedgehog      | hamster   |

