.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, golf, sailing, badminton
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, whist, poker
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | skateboarding | sailing | golf | badminton   |
| Game     | whist  | scrabble    | backgammon       | poker |

 